quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  7,109,"Abakungu mu bantu ba Firawo nebagamba nti mazima ono, mulogo kakensa"
  7,110,"Ayagala ku baggya mu nsi ya mmwe, kati mmwe kiki kye mugamba"
  7,111,"Nebagamba nti, mugambe ne mugandawe balindeko, otume mu bitundu byonna abakunga (abalogo)"
  7,112,Bajja kukuleetera buli mulogo omukugu
  7,113,"Era abalogo bajja ewa Firawo ne bagamba nti, mazima tuteekwa okusasulwa, kavuna tuba nga ffe tuwangudde"
  7,114,"Naagamba nti weewaawo, era mazima ddala mujja kubeera mu abo abambeera ku lusegere"
  7,115,"Nebagamba nti owange Musa ggwe osooka okwanja, oba ffe tusooka okussaawo"
  7,116,"Naagamba nti musseewo, bwe bassaawo baaloga amaaso g’abantu, era nebabatiisa nnyo, anti baaleeta e ddogo e pitirivu"
  7,117,"Netutumira Musa nti, suula omuggogwo, negutandika okumira byonna, ebyo bye baali bajingiridde"
  7,118,"Amazima negalabika, byonna bye baali bakola nebifa"
  7,119,"Bwe batyo nebawangulirwa awo wennyini, nebafuuka abakkakanyiziddwa"
  7,120,Bbo abalogo beesanga nga bateekwa kuvunnama
  7,121,Nebagamba nti tukkirizza Mukama Katonda omulabirizi w’ebitonde
  7,122,Mukama omulabirizi wa Musa ne Haruna
  7,123,"Firawo naagamba nti mumukkirizza nga sibawadde lukusa, (kirabika nti mazima ddala) luno lukwe lwe mwakoledde mu kitundu kino olw'ekigendererwa ky’okugobamu abantu baamu, naye muggya ku kimanya"
  7,124,"Nja kubatemako e mikono n’amagulu gammwe mu mpuyi ez’enjawulo (Nga bwetutema omukono ogwa ddyo, okugulu tutema kwa kkono) ate oluvanyuma mwenna nja kubakomerera ku misaalaba"
  7,125,"Nebagamba nti (ekyo temuli), anti mazima ddala ffe olwo tunaaba tudda eri Mukama omulabirizi waffe"
  7,126,"Tolina kyotuvunaana okugyako okuba nti tukkirizza e bigambo by’a Mukama omulabirizi waffe e bitujjidde, ayi Mukama omulabirizi waffe tugonnomoleko obugumiikiriza, era otuuse e ntuuko yaffe nga tuli basiraamu"